                    <div class="block-header green">
                        <h1>About</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="block-content">
                        <p>Named after our school mascot, the sabercat, SaberChat is a platform that connects and centralizes Alsion's various communication and notification platforms, streamlining communication between students, faculty, parents and more.</p>
                        <p>Users can quickly access any important information from faculty, communicate with others, order from the No Left Turn Caf√©, and access some of Alsion's unique projects.</p>
                        <p>Centralizing our school's content to an inclusive platform will improve our school's identity, as well as relationships between students, parents and faculty across the school.</p>
                        <em><strong>Developers: </strong>Alexander Zhou, Kabir Samsi, Siddharth Chavan, Vibhav Darsha</em>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 block">
                <img class="image-block" src="https://alsionschool.org/images/middle-school/MiddleSchoolMainPage.jpg" alt="fancy pic">
